headline.print_headline: Villa Sign French Fullback Cissokho From Valencia
headline.main: Villa Sign French Fullback Cissokho From Valencia

lead_paragraph: Aston Villa have signed left back Aly Cissokho from Valencia on a four-year deal subject to international clearance, the Premier League club announced on Friday.
